high_descs: Turn around and enter the room with the fridge, going towards the diningtable.
Pick up the bread from the table.
Turn and go to the fridge.
Put the bread in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Exit the room the way you came in and go straight ahead towards the oval coffeetable to the right.
Place the loaf of bread on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Cool a loaf of Bread in a fridge and place it on a CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Turn around and go into the room through the door on the left.
Pick up the bread on the table.
Go to the fridge on your left.
Put the bread in the refrigerator then take it back out.
Leave the room and go to the coffeetable in front of the couch.
Put the bread on the coffeetable on the far side.
anns.task_desc: Chill a loaf of Bread and put it on the CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Turn around to enter the dining room and walk to the diningtable.
Pick up the bread from the table.
Turn around to reach the fridge.
Cool the bread in the fridge and take it out.
Turn left to exit the room and walk straight to reach the coffeetable on the right.
Put the bread on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled bread on the CoffeeTable.
